snippet.description:
► Website: http://www.rammstein.com
► Shop: http://shop.rammstein.de

Premiere: September 2002
Shoot: 9th - 12th of January, 2002
Location: Prague
Director: Robert Cohen
Single: Feuer Frei!
From the album: Mutter

The FEUER FREI video was cut by Rob Cohen, the director of the Triple X movie, and is a montage of Rammstein's performance at the beginning of the movie, as well as snippets from the movie itself.
snippet.title: Rammstein - Feuer Frei! (Official Video)
